name: VoidFinity
description:
The game is simple : Collect all the coins of the level to go to the next, avoid the enemies and get the highest score ! Faster you go, better the score will be !

Controls :
  • Arrow Keys to move
  • R to restart in game
  • K to end the game

Note : There are sound effects in the game, so turn on the sound !
Have fun :) It's a little game that i've made to learn how to use Godot !

- MimStar
